Currently, this code has only been tested for Python 3.7+

To install, make sure that the parent directory of this README file
is in your Python search path, either by altering PYTHONPATH from the
shell or sys.path from inside the interpreter.  Then, 'import pytoon'.

For usage, please see the user guide in the Documentation directory.
